data.description: Nestled in the western suburbs you will find this charming, quaint ranch which offers so much potential to a buyer with a little vision and desire to create some real equity! This home is in the ideal location being just steps from I-290 and 294, it does not get more centrally located than this, the home offers a large open living room, two spacious bedrooms and a lower level which can be finished to add a third bedroom. The home is on a wider lot which is a plus, the private yard is also a plus! There are limited homes which has as much upside as this one in the community, do not overlook this or judge this one by its cover, get inside today to appreciate all this home has to offer
